    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal mechanical grip through the corners. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including the replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators to ensure the longevity of the high-tension internals. While the exterior and cabin show honest signs of use, the suspension geometry remains true, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback sought by purists. It is a mechanically sound example of BMW M\u2019s last atmospheric V8 era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
