    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of a well-loved driver and a meticulously maintained machine. The exterior finish retains a deep, reflective luster, showing only minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of careful daily use but barely noticeable from five feet away. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats remain supple with minimal bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracks. All electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is bone-dry and pulls strongly through every gear. I have strictly adhered to a 5,000-mile synthetic oil change interval, and the car recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection with flying colors. It sits on a set of Michelin tires with approximately 70% tread remaining and features recently replaced brake pads. This is a turn-key vehicle for a buyer who values mechanical integrity and a documented service history. Sold with two keys, the original owner's manuals, and a complete folder of maintenance receipts.",
